author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Shower sound deadening tips using Safe’n’Sound…I always want clients to have privacy in their bathrooms. Also, running water and drain pipes can send noise into adjacent rooms. For that reason I use Safe’n’Sound inside walls. It’s easy to install and one bundle goes a long way. Many thanks to Rockwool for sending product for this remodel 🔥#sounddeadening #showerremodel #bathroomremodel #rockwoolinsulation #brandpartner
